IMAPStore meain-remote
Host imap.gmail.com
Port  993
User abinsimon10@gmail.com
PassCmd "echo $GOOGLE_PASSWORD"
AuthMechs LOGIN
SSLType IMAPS

MaildirStore meain-local
Subfolders Verbatim
Path ~/.local/share/mail/meain/
Inbox ~/.local/share/mail/meain/INBOX
Flatten .

Channel meain
Create Both
Expunge Both
Far :meain-remote:
Near :meain-local:
# Patterns * !"[Gmail]/All Mail"
Patterns *
SyncState *
ExpireUnread yes
MaxMessages 500
